'''2013年津巴布韦大选'''於2013年7月31日举行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/zimbabwe-president-robert-mugabe-officially-proclaims-election-date-19391209#.Ubnfu9jc-UQ|title=Zimbabwe President Robert Mugabe Officially Proclaims New Election Date of July 31|last=|first=|date=13 June 2013|work=|location=|accessdate=13 June 2013}}</ref>，結果由執政33年的現任總統[[羅伯·穆加貝|羅伯·穆加比]]再度當選辛巴威總統，而其所屬的政黨[[辛巴威非洲民族聯盟—愛國陣線|辛巴威非洲民族聯盟—愛國陣線]]則在國會眾議院獲得三分之二以上的議席。反對派在結果宣布前已指責選舉舞弊，要求重選，又表明會循法律途徑推翻選舉結果<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=75402 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-08-04 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212072110/https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=75402 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
2013年3月，津巴布韦通过公民投票的形式对新宪法举行投票表决<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-21845444 Zimbabwe approves new constitution] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-21845444 |date=20191030222704 }} BBC News, 19 March 2013</ref>；5月22日，总统罗伯特·穆加贝签署生效<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/05/2013522105015147596.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2020-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906224819/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/05/2013522105015147596.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月31日津巴布韦最高法院裁定，穆加贝总统应该尽快设定一个日期，总统和议会选举必须在7月31日举行，法院随后以程序的形式执行<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-22728189 Zimbabwe elections 'must be held by 31 July'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-22728189 |date=20201112000505 }} BBC News, 31 May 2013</ref>。根据新宪法，总统选举的获胜者将有五年总统任期<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/may/31/robert-mugabe-elections-july-zimbabwe-court |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130716015242/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/may/31/robert-mugabe-elections-july-zimbabwe-court |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

